OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will clear from the west this
OL,7,Fevening. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be dry with broken cloud.
OL,9,FFreshening southerly winds later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FCloudy start with a little
OL,12,Frain. Then becoming drier with a few
OL,13,Fbright or sunny intervals and just the
OL,14,Fodd shower.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FWednesday will be a showery day with
OL,18,Fstrong to gale force winds. Thursday
OL,19,Fcloudy with rain, heavy at times,
OL,20,Fbrighter later. Friday brighter with a
OL,21,Ffew showers, less windy.
